description: We’re putting the PRO back in PROTEIN! Plus, the one PROTEIN find Lisa is LOVING right now! Did we mention this episode is PACKED with PROTEIN?! (IT IS!) [hungry-girl.com/protein](hungry-girl.com/protein)
